                                <locus from="SL1r" to="SL1r" scheme="folios"/>
                                <note>Upper part of page, in brown ink by a 19th century hand: <quote>Jacobi de Voragine Speculum de Beata Virgine (Sermones CLI.)</quote>; centre page: National Library stamp.</note>
                            </p>
